    # rebecca "I thought if we won the [HanaHanaFruit.n] fruit, we could become strong enough to free [Dressrosa.n] from [donflamingo.n]."
    rebecca "Pensei que se ganhássemos a fruta [HanaHanaFruit.n], poderíamos ficar fortes o suficiente para libertar [Dressrosa.n] de [donflamingo.n]."

