    # narrador "I let my gaze drop meaningfully to my waist, then back up to her eyes."
    narrador "Deixei meu olhar descer significativamente até minha cintura, e depois voltei a encará-la."

# game/scripts/Events/Locations/Dressrosa/dressrosa_h14.rpy:111
