    # player "We really are close by now... we've been through so many things... and you really do feel good with me, right?"
    player "Estamos muito próximos agora... passamos por tantas coisas... e você realmente se sente bem comigo, não é?"

# game/scripts/Events/Locations/Dressrosa/dressrosa_h14.rpy:113
